title: The Incomplete
creator_credit: Zdenka Doycheva and State Distribution Centre
brief_description: A little boy is drawing happily when, suddenly, the telephone rings. While the artist is away a feud develops between the two animated figures. Just as one is about to pronounce himself victorious, the boy returns and quickly provides a happy ending for all. No commentary - music and sound effects only.
